{"tid":1468994,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"係微博search付國豪，我見到恐怖既獨裁","createTime":"2019-08-13T23:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:24:55.000Z","uid":252840,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"215fa734818d56d13349f048764e8346d1003e45","tid":1468994,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:59:01.000Z","msg":"當你係微博search付國豪，或者有人見到既係中國人都好愛國支持共產黨，但我見到既係一個獨裁政府操控輿論既結果。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係心理學家，我淨係知一樣米養百樣人，一個正常既社會，無可能所有人睇法都類似，你睇我地香港社會有黃絲有藍絲，有勇武有和理飛有冷氣軍師，我地好多唔同意見，努力係一片混亂中達到共識。<br />\n<br />\n係，我地咁樣好無效率，爭完一大輪都未做到野，但我地尊重自由意志，尊重言論自由，尊重每一個人既人權。咁先係自然發展既民主社會應有既表現。<br />\n<br />\n係微博上面，我睇到只有單一既風向，只有一種言論，而中國仍然好多人沉醉係呢種獨裁政府洗人民腦既英雄主義，呢個係我覺得中國政府最可怕又最成功既地方。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地更加要保護好香港，呢個混亂而又自由美麗既地方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/075639_4f94ea73f8e6566f8242c7d4fb880a9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F075639_4f94ea73f8e6566f8242c7d4fb880a9e.jpg&h=921032ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7db48a42c4803be7606f8844f980acbdeb626225","tid":1468994,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nn8VVzp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNn8VVzp.png&h=a9edb110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n派一個公安、一個記者，再夾埋幾個牛屎飛做一場戲<br />\n<br />\n咁聽日大陸就會全部播呢啲片<br />\n<br />\n大陸人就會好憎香港人<br />\n<br />\n因為中共最驚就係大陸人支援香港人<br />\n<br />\n我哋要諗吓點爭取大陸人支持<br />\n<br />\n只要有1%大陸人支持我哋，中共就仆街"},{"pid":"dac29c52f5ee27c3b17dfeaa9c5140d3d570660b","tid":1468994,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:02:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"665137989ae61b07786f43b0f80c09c08f4a6179","tid":1468994,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:02:50.000Z","msg":"如果同樣情況，喺大陸當眾俾人發現係幫反中亂港胖子黎工作嘅毒果記者，應該都唔會好得去邊"},{"pid":"3730a52db9c23531af841f705f749dbb5c6f9f41","tid":1468994,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:07:30.000Z","msg":"由於幅圖太長，請入下面條link睇<br />\n<br />\nbrainwashing <a href=\"https://imgur.com/gallery/G4xWj7p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fgallery%2FG4xWj7p&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=7f5c898b\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/gallery/G4xWj7p</a>"},{"pid":"967f125a3ec9aa367dfa02cf80b0b7c3443320e4","tid":1468994,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:10:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dd27371c0d3035db3f0548112e590b38cf4d984","tid":1468994,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:16:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65a0b07607231bd4c10960d32e091e67bf14e617","tid":1468994,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:24:55.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}